:HELP NAME='OMH055C1/S1OPTN'.Route Maintenance - Help

:P.
:XH3.Option

:P.
Use this column to perform different operations on individual
entries. Type the option number next to an entry and press Enter. You
can type the same option next to more than one entry at a time, and
you can also type different options next to different entries at the
same time. The possible values are:

:PARML.
:PT.2=Change
:PD.
Type 2 to change the attributes of the Entity.

:PT.4=Delete
:PD.
Type 4 to delete the Entity.
:EPARML.

